tly what we do not want anyone to do with AI.\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1322, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 4.3677762977779635e-12, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"concern\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"the intended message\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"the ad\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1254}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1285}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1307}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ever.\\\"\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Professor Shelley was especially critical of Google's ad, deliberately making \\\"misleading promises of AI's capabilities.\\\"\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1341, \"end\": 1348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\", \"score\": 0.999965524897714, \"rank\": 3.4476290872332087e-05, \"text\": \"Shelley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\"}, {\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"score\": 0.9998481937848054, \"rank\": 0.0001518292615539078, \"text\": \"Google\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Google\"}, {\"begin\": 1433, \"end\": 1435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 4.3677762977779635e-12, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"misleading promises\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In relation to this concern, Shelley said: \\\"The commercial suggests that a poorly worded prompt, processed by a pattern-matching autocomplete algorithm, can empower an LLM to articulate a person's feelings better than the person themselves.\\\"\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\", \"score\": 0.999965524897714, \"rank\": 3.4476290872332087e-05, \"text\": \"Shelley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/List_of_South_Park_families\"}, {\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\", \"score\": 0.9999999999517968, \"rank\": 4.8155467498264254e-11, \"text\": \"LLM\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Master_of_Laws\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"relation\", \"from\": 1457, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"this concern\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"The commercial\", \"from\": 1498, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"a poorly worded prompt\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1549}, {\"ngram\": \"a pattern-matching autocomplete algorithm\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"a person's feelings\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1659}, {\"ngram\": \"the person\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This once again brings communications experts' concerns over the use of AI for personal tasks such as letter writing to the forefront.\", \"from\": 1697, \"to\": 1831, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1769, \"end\": 1771, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999945